Two people were killed by members of the community after
being  accused of terrorising the
communities of Makhando and Thohoyandou in Limpopo.Police spokesperson Colonel Moatshe Ngoepe said It is
alleged that at about 13:30 in Tshino location outside Thohoyandou on Wednesday,
a group of community members cornered three suspected criminals along the
street and accused them of being responsible for the spate of burglaries, house
robberies as well as rapes in and around the area.He said they assaulted them using various objects and
